 Mosque is one hundred times better than prayer in this mosque\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26118,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/26\/women-adab-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":27465,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: Women having proper etiquette in the mosque","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 26, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amrah bint Abdur Rahman reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \u201cWere the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, to see what women are now doing, he would have prevented them from attending the mosque, just as the women of the children of Israel were\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13995,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/06\/every-step-mosque-rewarded\/","url_meta":{"origin":27465,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Mosques: Every step to mosque for prayer is rewarded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever purifies himself with ablution in his house, then he walks to a house among the houses of Allah to fulfill an obligation among the obligations of Allah, one step of his will expiate his sins\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\